<C>__{ralph}
<D>__{rocky the fighting stallone.}
<P>__{(on her blank look)}
<C>__{ralph}
<D>__{i keep forgetting you just left the twilight zone. hey, why don't you come up to my room, and i will bring you up to date. i've got a vhs vcr, a cd, and mtv.}
<C>__{cynthia}
<D>__{you're making this up... aren't you?}
<A>__{he just grins. she slips down to the floor, does some stretching exercises.}
<C>__{cynthia }
<D>__{sounds like a complicated world. how do you handle it?}
